title: Queue Time are insane.
body: Last few weeks the queue times for normal games for me have been around 22-25 minutes and the blood moon playlist its queues have been around 15-17 minutes. I was just wondering if its just where maybe you've had a lot of log ins or what but its seriously insane i have to wait 15-17 minutes for a 15-20 minute game.

replies.body: It's because there's not too many people pre-30 playing much atm
If you're playing with this account; the main reason for that is because you are not level 30. The game has a hard time placing you with others when the majority of the population is level 30.
